                      "important_understanding":  "Correlative conjunction: pair में काम करता है। Conjunction vs Preposition Conjunction clauses/words जोड़ता है। Example: I was tired but I worked. Preposition noun/pronoun से relation दिखाता है। Example: He sat on the chair. Conjunction vs Relative Pronoun Relative Pronoun noun + clause जोड़ता है। Example: The boy who came here is my friend. Conjunction दो clauses जोड़ता है। Example: I came because you called me. Relative pronoun: noun का relation बनाता है। Conjunction: clause connection बनाता है। Common Conjunction Functions FunctionConjunction Additionand Contrastbut Choiceor Causebecause Conditionif Timewhen Resultso Multiple Conjunction Example Although he was tired, he continued working because he wanted success. Explanation although → contrast because → cause एक sentence में: एक से अधिक conjunction हो सकते हैं। Common Mistakes ❌ Because he was ill. → incomplete sentence ✅ He stayed home because he was ill. ❌ Although he is rich but unhappy. ✅ Although he is rich, he is unhappy. ✅ He is rich but unhappy. Conjunction and Sentence Building Conjunction: simple sentences को: longer smoother logical बनाता है। Example Simple Ram came. Mohan came. With Conjunction Ram and Mohan came. Small Advanced Awareness Modern grammar में: कुछ conjunctions को: coordinating markers subordinators discourse connectors जैसे नामों से भी पढ़ाया जाता है। आगे advanced grammar में इसकी awareness मिलेगी। ",
